    Chunk, ChunkDataListType, ChunkDataListTypeLabeledText

    public class ChunkDataListTypeLabeledTextImpl
extends ChunkDataListTypeImpl
implements ChunkDataListTypeLabeledText
    An implementation of the model object 'Chunk Data List Type Labeled Text'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Sample Length
    • Purpose ID
    • Country
    • Language
    • Dialect
    • Code Page
